text: Norwegian Wood may mean: * "Norwegian Wood (This Bird Has Flown)", a 1965 song by the Beatles * Norwegian Wood (music festival), an annual music festival in Oslo, Norway * Norwegian Wood (novel), a novel by Haruki Murakami 1987 ** Norwegian Wood (movie), a movie by Tran Anh Hung, based on the Murakami novel * For woodland in Norway, see Geography of Norway#Flora
title: Norwegian Wood
